data.title: Ken Gillespie
data.meta_description: Ken Gillespie is an internationally experienced Commercial Director and strategic thinker with a technology and publishing focused track record.
data.text:
Ken is an internationally experienced Commercial Director and strategic thinker with a technology and publishing focused track record.

He has gained broad commercial experience in B2B sectors and industries including geospatial, digital, publishing and e-commerce. Ken is an outstanding leader of people and has successfully built teams across Australia, Europe and North America.
